sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant F as Vue 前端
  participant G as Gateway
  participant Pay as mall-pay
  participant MQ as RocketMQ
  participant O as mall-order
  participant I as mall-inventory

  F->>G: POST /api/v1/pay/create
  G->>Pay: 创建支付单
  Pay-->>F: 返回支付流水
  F->>G: 模拟支付成功
  G->>Pay: 支付成功通知
  Pay->>MQ: PAY_RESULT(orderNo, paid)
  MQ->>O: 消费并 markPaid
  MQ->>I: 消费并 confirmDeduct
  O-->>MQ: 幂等处理完成
  I-->>MQ: 幂等处理完成
